<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hold-n">hold <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /həʊld/    美 /hoʊld/  </p>
<p>[U] [可用单数]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>拿着；抓住；握住：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She tried to <strong>keep hold of</strong> the child's hand as they walked along.
走路时她尽力拉住孩子的手。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Make sure you've got a steady hold on the camera.
确保把相机拿稳。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="catch-get-take-a-hold-of">catch / get / take (a) hold of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>抓住；拿着；握住：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Take hold of that end to help me move this table.
抬桌子那头，帮我把它移开。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Most of my childhood was spent on books I could get hold of. 
童年的大部分时间我都在阅读我能得到的书籍。</p><footer>2010 四川改</footer></div>

<h3 id="get-hold-of-sb">get hold of sb</h3>
<p>1.<strong>和某人联系；找到某人：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have been trying to get hold of you all afternoon.
我整个下午都在找你。</p><footer>2017 全国</footer></div>

<h3 id="get-hold-of-sth">get hold of sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>找到 / 得到所需要的东西；学会 / 理解某事物</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="on-hold">on hold</h3>
<p>1.<strong>中断；推迟：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>While matters of money won't be settled for weeks, Jane hardly puts her project on hold.
虽然几周的时间也将无法解决钱的问题，但简不会中断自己的项目。</p><footer>2010 四川改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>holder /'həʊldə(r)/ n <br />
holding /'həʊldɪŋ/ n   </p>
<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>As a grassroots singer, she reads everything she can get hold <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ concerning music, and takes every opportunity to improve herself.  （2014 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. of  </p></div>